y, Says Anambra Hasn&#8217;t Seen Anything Yet</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-e0f918913530e9b1 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container featured-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="EIU Report: FG to Raise VAT to 15% By 2027 to Fund Fiscal Deficit" href="eiu-report-fg-to-raise-vat-to-15-by-2027-to-fund-fiscal-deficit5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/EIU.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-share"><amp-social-share layout="responsive" width="25" height="25" type="system" aria-label="Share" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de share-system i-amphtml-layout-responsive i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="responsive"><i-amphtml-sizer style="display:block;padding-top:100%"></i-amphtml-sizer></amp-social-share></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="EIU Report: FG to Raise VAT to 15% By 2027 to Fund Fiscal Deficit" href="eiu-report-fg-to-raise-vat-to-15-by-2027-to-fund-fiscal-deficit5593?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">EIU Report: FG to Raise VAT to 15% By 2027 to Fund Fiscal Deficit</h3></a></div></article></div></div></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 next-category-articles"><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 header"><span class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 title">Business</span></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 container"><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="El-Yakub’s Inelegant Disquisition on Yemi Cardoso, Mele Kyari" href="../23/el-yakubs-inelegant-disquisition-on-yemi-cardoso-mele-kyari5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Kyari.jpeg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="El-Yakub’s Inelegant Disquisition on Yemi Cardoso, Mele Kyari" href="../23/el-yakubs-inelegant-disquisition-on-yemi-cardoso-mele-kyari5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">El-Yakub’s Inelegant Disquisition on Yemi Cardoso, Mele Kyari</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="  SETTING GLOBAL STANDARDS FOR GENDER EQUALITY" href="../23/setting-global-standards-for-gender-equality5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/CSW_Banner.png" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="  SETTING GLOBAL STANDARDS FOR GENDER EQUALITY" href="../23/setting-global-standards-for-gender-equality5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">  SETTING GLOBAL STANDARDS FOR GENDER EQUALITY</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Carima: Streamlining African Car Market" href="../23/carima-streamlining-african-car-market5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Pix-3.jpeg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-55